# Day 7 – Basic Network Scanning

## Objective
Perform a basic network scan using Nmap and identify open ports.

## Tools Used
- Kali Linux
- Nmap

## Commands Used

```bash
python3 -m http.server 8000
nmap localhost
```

## Result
Successfully scanned the local machine using Nmap and identified the open port:

- 8000/tcp – Open (HTTP Server)

